<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 13:47:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>科学家绘制了流感病毒如何从内部重新连接人体细胞的图谱</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-map-how-the-flu-virus-rewires-the-human-cell-from-the-inside</link><description>汉堡 EMBL 的研究人员和莱布尼茨分子药理学研究所 (FMP) 的合作者以前所未有的详细程度绘制了甲型流感病毒如何重新连接受感染的人类细胞的图谱。为此，研究人员使用定制的实验工作流程来直接观察蛋白质如何在完整的感染细胞内相互作用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-map-how-the-flu-virus-rewires-the-human-cell-from-the-inside.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 13:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-map-how-the-flu-virus-rewires-the-human-cell-from-the-inside</guid></item><item><title>炎症性肠病已在芯片上重现，科学家终于可以找出其原因</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/inflammatory-bowel-disease-has-been-recreated-on-a-chip-and-scientists-could-finally-figure-out-its-cause</link><description>炎症性肠病影响着全世界数百万人，但科学家们仍然不完全了解是什么导致了损害肠道的慢性炎症。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/inflammatory-bowel-disease-has-been-recreated-on-a-chip-and-scientists-could-finally-figure-out-its-cause.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 13:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/inflammatory-bowel-disease-has-been-recreated-on-a-chip-and-scientists-could-finally-figure-out-its-cause</guid></item><item><title>大卫·辛普森谈《后人类》、《超人类》和《弑神者》</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/david-simpson-on-posthuman-transhuman-and-the-god-killers</link><description>&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/david-simpson-on-posthuman-transhuman-and-the-god-killers2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 13:17:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/david-simpson-on-posthuman-transhuman-and-the-god-killers</guid></item><item><title>薛定谔的蚁丘：在大到足以容纳的晶体中发现量子纠缠</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/schrodingers-anthill-quantum-entanglement-found-in-a-crystal-large-enough-to-hold</link><description>科学家们在手掌大小的晶体内发现了令人惊讶的强量子纠缠，揭示了即使是宏观材料也可以以深刻的量子方式表现。厘米大小的晶体揭示了量子纠缠的明显迹象，表明大型日常物体可以表现出令人惊讶的深层量子行为。这一发现可能有助于解开奇怪金属之谜，同时为超精密量子传感器和其他先进技术开辟新的可能性。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/schrodingers-anthill-quantum-entanglement-found-in-a-crystal-large-enough-to-hold.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 13:02:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/schrodingers-anthill-quantum-entanglement-found-in-a-crystal-large-enough-to-hold</guid></item><item><title>Selfimprovingagent/AwesomeSelfImprovingAgents：基于基础模型的代理系统中自我改进的精选列表</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/selfimprovingagent-awesomeselfimprovingagents-a-curated-list-for-selfimprovement-in-foundation-model-based-agentic-systems</link><description>基于基础模型的代理系统自我改进的精选列表。 — 自我改进代理/很棒的自我改进代理&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/selfimprovingagent-awesomeselfimprovingagents-a-curated-list-for-selfimprovement-in-foundation-model-based-agentic-systems2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 12:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/selfimprovingagent-awesomeselfimprovingagents-a-curated-list-for-selfimprovement-in-foundation-model-based-agentic-systems</guid></item><item><title>新的基于拓扑的生物标志物可以改善乳腺癌预测</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/new-topology-based-biomarkers-may-improve-breast-cancer-prediction</link><description>几十年来，病理学家通过在显微镜下观察组织样本，寻找细胞和组织结构紊乱的迹象来诊断和分级乳腺癌。现在，哥伦比亚大学的研究人员及其合作者开发了一种新的计算方法，可以将这些视觉模式转化为定量测量，从而有可能改善临床医生预测乳腺癌结果和选择治疗方法的方式。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-topology-based-biomarkers-may-improve-breast-cancer-prediction2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 12:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/new-topology-based-biomarkers-may-improve-breast-cancer-prediction</guid></item><item><title>血液 p-tau217 水平在症状出现前数年就预示着认知障碍风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/blood-p-tau217-levels-signal-cognitive-impairment-risk-years-before-symptoms-emerge</link><description>在 2,684 名认知未受损的成年人中，较高的基线血浆 p-tau217 与较高的 5 年和 10 年认知障碍风险以及较快的认知衰退相关。非常高的水平相当于五年内估计的 38% 风险，但选定的队列和有限的长期数据意味着常规筛查和个体化预测仍然为时过早。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/blood-p-tau217-levels-signal-cognitive-impairment-risk-years-before-symptoms-emerge.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 12:17:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/blood-p-tau217-levels-signal-cognitive-impairment-risk-years-before-symptoms-emerge</guid></item><item><title>“2000 年代中期是第一人称射击游戏的黄金时代”：《Dusk》和《Iron Lung》的创作者 David Szymanski 在他的 PC 上讨论这些游戏</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-mid2000s-was-the-golden-era-of-firstperson-shooters-david-szymanski-creator-of-dusk-and-iron-lung-discusses-the-games-on-his-pc</link><description>大卫·西曼斯基，创造者&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-mid2000s-was-the-golden-era-of-firstperson-shooters-david-szymanski-creator-of-dusk-and-iron-lung-discusses-the-games-on-his-pc.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 12:02:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-mid2000s-was-the-golden-era-of-firstperson-shooters-david-szymanski-creator-of-dusk-and-iron-lung-discusses-the-games-on-his-pc</guid></item><item><title>等离子体尾场加速中正电子的自适应追赶注入</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/self-adaptive-catch-up-injection-of-positrons-in-plasma-wakefield-acceleration</link><description>等离子体尾场加速中的有效正电子注入具有挑战性，因为它需要既能聚焦又能加速正电子的场结构。在这里，我们提出了一种自适应追赶注入方案，其中放置在空心带正电驱动器前面的正电子源在尾流赶上时被自然捕获。分析建模和 3D PIC 模拟表明，具有广泛初始条件的正电子可以注入类似的加速阶段，并进一步加速到多 GeV 能量。这些结果为等离子体尾场中的新正电子注入和加速方案提供了原理验证演示。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/self-adaptive-catch-up-injection-of-positrons-in-plasma-wakefield-acceleration2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 11:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/self-adaptive-catch-up-injection-of-positrons-in-plasma-wakefield-acceleration</guid></item><item><title>研究地球开花植物的科学家向人类发出严厉警告</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-studying-earths-flowering-plants-issue-a-stark-warning-to-humanity</link><description>从&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-studying-earths-flowering-plants-issue-a-stark-warning-to-humanity.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 11:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-studying-earths-flowering-plants-issue-a-stark-warning-to-humanity</guid></item></channel></rss>